p: \rHe tore through me and my team. If you fight him... this might be your toughest challenge yet, \pn.
\bOur mistress has instructed us to bring you to her.\nYou better have your shards of the crystal ready. That's what this is all about.
\bThis world and the Distortion World are like two sides of a coin, except one coin is much smaller, empty, and full of dangers.\nHardly sounds fair, does it?
